{
  "stem": "1479.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can never forgive or understand how there [? not ?] over there were women working in this barrack.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How, like sadists-- so sadistically, when they saw a tall woman, they would throw something, just a small piece of clothing, just barely to cover their body.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And yet, when they saw a short woman, they would throw something warm and long, a-- a bigger garment.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we were only in the wooden shoes, bare feet, no socks, nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Over there, they gave us such rags, I would say.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we looked horrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from there, we march-- they marched us to a barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When we arrived in this barrack, always the 300 women separately, they brought us-- after two and a half days-- they brought us the black coffee.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was our first nourishment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we thought-- we felt-- that not only what the Nazis did to us, but hopelessness entered, because you thought cannot survive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You cannot go on with life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What we experienced, short-- in such a short time enough, it's-- and this was very scary, sad, when you were losing hope.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "However, we went through plenty in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Mengele did selections and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Thank god, because the whole world knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They knew very well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They did nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Schindler did not rest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He tried to do the impossible thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was sending people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was, himself, intervening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was determined in asking for his 300 women.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was not simple.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yet he was so determined that he succeeded, because after a few weeks in Auschwitz, there came the order.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, they picked us over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gave us some food before we left.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
